// ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
const _CG_HANJA=["甲","乙","丙","丁","戊","己","庚","辛","壬","癸"];
const _JJ_HANJA=["子","丑","寅","卯","辰","巳","午","未","申","酉","戌","亥"];
const _JJ_KR=["자","축","인","묘","진","사","오","미","신","유","술","해"];
const _CG_COLORS=["#7CB87B","#7CB87B","#E85555","#E85555","#C8834A","#C8834A","#D4AF37","#D4AF37","#4A90D9","#4A90D9"];
const _SAJU_LOADING=["천간지지 배열 중... ☯️","용신 계산 중... 🔥","신살 분석 중... ⚡","합충 관계 점검 중... 🌊","20만원짜리 점집보다 정확하게 분석 중... 💎","대운 흐름 추적 중... 🔄","개운법 처방 중... ✨"];

function _sajuPillars(birth:string,timeStr?:string){
  const parts=birth?birth.replace(/[^0-9]/g,"-").split("-").filter(Boolean):[];
  const y=+(parts[0]||1990),m=+(parts[1]||1),d=+(parts[2]||1);
  const hour=timeStr&&timeStr!=="모름"?parseInt(timeStr):null;
  const s=_getSaju(y,m,d,hour);
  const ohang=_getOhang(s);
  const ilOh=_CG_OHANG[s.ilgan];
  // v807(Phase2): 격국·용신·신살을 정통 엔진(억부)으로 — 구 max/min 오행 추정 폐기
  const eng=computeSaju(birth,timeStr??null);
  const gyeokguk=eng.gyeokguk;
  const yongsin=eng.yongsin;
  const pillars=[
    {label:"시주",cg:s.hour?s.hour.cg:0,jj:s.hour?s.hour.jj:0,hl:false,exists:!!s.hour},
    {label:"일주",cg:s.day.cg,jj:s.day.jj,hl:true,exists:true},
    {label:"월주",cg:s.month.cg,jj:s.month.jj,hl:false,exists:true},
    {label:"연주",cg:s.year.cg,jj:s.year.jj,hl:false,exists:true},
  ];
  return{pillars,ohang,ilgan:s.ilgan,ilOh,gyeokguk,yongsin,gangyak:eng.gangyak,gangyakScore:eng.gangyakScore,yongsinReason:eng.yongsinReason,engSinsal:eng.sinsal,year:y,month:m,day:d,hour};
}

